subSubSection.paragraph:
Pedipalp
(
Fig. 17
). Trichobothrial pattern orthobothriotaxic, 
Type
A (
Vachon 1974
). Dorsal trichobothria on femur in β (beta) configuration (
Vachon, 1975
). Femur pentacarinate, all carinae crenulate. Patella with 7 smooth carinae. Dentate margins on fixed and movable fingers with 9 imbricate rows of granules; external accessory granule moderate.
